	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## LLM Workflow for Alfred 5

Quick access to LLM APIs (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, OpenRouter) for freeform Q&amp;A and text transformations.

### Setup
1. Set API keys in workflow environment variables:
   - OPENAI_API_KEY
   - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
   - GEMINI_API_KEY
   - OPENROUTER_API_KEY

2. Use `llm-model` to select your preferred model.

### Usage
- `ask &lt;prompt&gt;` — freeform question, response copied to clipboard
- `ask-more &lt;prompt&gt;` — continue previous conversation
- `llm-model` — select the active model
- Select text → Universal Action → "Send to LLM" → pick a template

### Custom Templates
Drop `.txt` files in the `templates/` folder with frontmatter:
```
---
name: My Template
output: clipboard|paste|largetype
system: Optional system prompt
---
Your prompt here with {{input}} placeholder
```</string>
